readme:
# scp-syntax package

Syntax for SCP language which is used in OSTIS

## Installing
#### On the command line:
```ssh
apm install scp-atom-syntax
```
#### On Atom:
Go to `Preferences > Install`, search for `scp-atom-syntax` and install it.
